channel.description:
I started SPR Productions in 2009 with a goal to explore the world of online Music and Video, and to create a platform for artists and myself to produce high quality YouTube Content and share their talent. Since then it has grown by leaps and bounds. From Phony Business to The Profile Picture Song, from my old Justin Bieber covers to Malls of Dubai. I have also had the opportunity to collaborate with several talented artists who I've learnt a lot from.

When it comes to instruments, I play the Guitar and Keyboard by ear and I'm a self taught Drummer. Behind the scenes I write, compose, arrange, perform, record, produce, film, edit and  post-produce Music and Video.

I love to experiment with different styles, from Rock to Rap, Marimba to Piano, Comedy to Action and much more! I also love other cultures and explore music in several languages, including fake ones hehe!

Thank you for subscribing and I hope you enjoy it here :D
Rohit Iyengar
CEO and Founder
